<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Classic Platformer — Games Landing</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<style>
  :root {
    --sky: #5c94fc;
    --sky-deep: #2347a1;
    --brick: #d96a3a;
    --brick-dark: #8a3814;
    --grass: #00a86b;
    --coin: #ffcc00;
    --ink: #1a1325;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; image-rendering: pixelated; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--sky) 0%, #87b8ff 60%, var(--grass) 60%, #006a3a 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 40px 24px 80px;
    color: var(--ink);
    position: relative;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  body::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 22%, #fff 0 12px, transparent 13px),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 18% 20%, #fff 0 14px, transparent 15px),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 21% 24%, #fff 0 10px, transparent 11px),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 78% 18%, #fff 0 14px, transparent 15px),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 82% 20%, #fff 0 12px, transparent 13px),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 16%, #fff 0 10px, transparent 11px);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  header { text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .hud {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 24px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #000;
  }
  .hud span:nth-child(odd) { color: var(--coin); }
  h1 {
    margin: 22px 0 8px;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 7vw, 80px);
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow:
      4px 4px 0 var(--brick-dark),
      8px 8px 0 var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .sub { color: var(--ink); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; }
  nav { margin-top: 20px; }
  nav a {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #000;
  }
  .grid {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .block {
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--brick) 0%, var(--brick-dark) 100%);
    border: 4px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 16px;
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--ink);
    position: relative;
  }
  .block::before, .block::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 6px; bottom: 6px;
    width: 4px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  }
  .block::before { left: 32%; }
  .block::after { left: 66%; }
  .shot-frame {
    background: #000;
    border: 3px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .shot {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    object-fit: cover;
    background: var(--sky-deep);
  }
  .coin-row {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: flex; gap: 6px;
  }
  .coin {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 14px; height: 14px;
    background: var(--coin);
    border: 2px solid var(--brick-dark);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: inset -2px -2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 2px 0 var(--brick-dark);
  }
  h2 {
    color: #fffce0;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--brick-dark);
  }
  .prompt {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    min-height: 90px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .play {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--coin);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 3px solid var(--ink);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--ink);
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .play:hover { transform: translate(2px, 2px); box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--ink); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="hud">
      <span>WORLD</span><span>1-1</span>
      <span>×</span><span>06</span>
      <span>COINS</span><span>×06</span>
      <span>TIME</span><span>∞∞∞</span>
    </div>
    <h1>PLATFORMER</h1>
    <div class="sub">SIX CLASSIC JUMP-AND-RUN ADVENTURES</div>
    <nav><a href="index.html">← ALL THEMES</a></nav>
  </header>

  <main class="grid">
    <article class="block">
      <div class="shot-frame"><a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/pixel-runner"><img class="shot" src="https://pixel-runner--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a></div>
      <div class="coin-row"><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span></div>
      <h2>JUMP BLOCKS</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Side-scrolling platformer with a chunky square hero. Brick platforms, coin pickups, spike pits, three short levels in NES palette.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/pixel-runner">▶ Play</a>
    </article>

    <article class="block">
      <div class="shot-frame"><a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/cave-gem-runner"><img class="shot" src="https://cave-gem-runner--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a></div>
      <div class="coin-row"><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span></div>
      <h2>CAVE COINS</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Cave platformer with swooping bats and sparkling gems. Double-jump unlocks after the first gem. Parallax cave backdrop, dripping stalactites.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/cave-gem-runner">▶ Play</a>
    </article>

    <article class="block">
      <div class="shot-frame"><a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/rainbow-ascent"><img class="shot" src="https://rainbow-ascent--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a></div>
      <div class="coin-row"><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span></div>
      <h2>SKY SPRINT</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Cloud-hopping race: clouds dissolve one second after you land. Reach the rainbow goal up top. Procedurally arranged clouds each run.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/rainbow-ascent">▶ Play</a>
    </article>

    <article class="block">
      <div class="shot-frame"><a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/stone-keep-run"><img class="shot" src="https://stone-keep-run--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a></div>
      <div class="coin-row"><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span></div>
      <h2>CASTLE QUEST</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Moving stone platforms, arcing fireballs, one slime per level you defeat by jumping on it. Five short levels, eight-bit chiptune.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/stone-keep-run">▶ Play</a>
    </article>

    <article class="block">
      <div class="shot-frame"><a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/acorn-bounce"><img class="shot" src="https://acorn-bounce--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a></div>
      <div class="coin-row"><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span></div>
      <h2>MUSHROOM LEAP</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Bouncy mushroom caps launch the hero very high. Collect ten golden acorns across stacked platforms. Pixel-art trees foreground and back.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/acorn-bounce">▶ Play</a>
    </article>

    <article class="block">
      <div class="shot-frame"><a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/frostbound-run"><img class="shot" src="https://frostbound-run--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a></div>
      <div class="coin-row"><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span><span class="coin"></span></div>
      <h2>SNOWY SLIDE</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Slippery ice, conveyor-belt snowdrifts that push you, icicles falling when you pass underneath. Earmuff hero, cool blue-and-white palette.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/frostbound-run">▶ Play</a>
    </article>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
